title: 820-00426 all works but no keyboard
message:
Hi,

Unit came in for keyboard replacement due to sticky keys issue. Replaced the palmrest as well as touchpad and battery as it started swelling. Now all but the keyboard works (power button still fine). I thought that the new palmrest was bad, but the old keyboard doesnt work at all either. No visible damage anywhere. Any pointers?

title: 820-00426 all works but no keyboard
message: BTW, cleaned the connector, tried the key combinations like NVram reset during boot but no response, no key apart of power button works
